Text-Mint

This is a pre-release version of Text::Mint. Only the tokenizer
module, Text::Mint::Tokenizer, is usable (but it works just fine).

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


